20 MINUTES FROM THE SQUARE IN CHARLOTTE<br>
Are you looking for home maintenance free living? Welcome to McCall Properties Inc., Pines MHP is one of our mobile home communities located in Gastonia NC that has been servicing the community for over 50 years.<br>
We have a 2 bedroom 2 bathroom mobile home unit for rent for $850.00 per month. This unit is spacious, sunny and one of our top energy efficient units. The kitchen/dining room area has beautiful pendant lighting and the living room features bay windows. The laundry area with hookups for both washer and dryer is located in the main bathroom.  The primary bedroom has a full bathroom attached to it with a tub/shower combination.  Off street parking is located in the front of the unit. Rent includes stove, refrigerator, water and sewer. We have a company that picks up trash on Tuesday and a person who mows the lawns. Tenant is responsible for electricity supplied by Duke Energy. <br>
NO PETS ALLOWED<br>
Qualifications: No felonies or evictions. Net monthly pay must be 3x greater that rent amount. A copy of current paystub with year to date totals is required. Must have 3 years current rental history where you are named on a lease or mortgage.  Application fee is $50.00 per adult and payable in money orders only.  RENT $850.00  SECURITY DEPOSIT $850.00<br>
IF APPROVED 1ST MONTHS RENT, SECURITY DEPOSIT AND KEY DEPOSIT ARE DUE AT LEASE SIGNING. WE REQUIRE ALL NEW TENANTS TO HAVE RENTERS INSURANCE AND A COPY OF THE DECLARATION PAGE MUST BE SUPPLIED.<br>
NO PETS ALLOWED<br>
For more information on this property, please go to z.i.l.l.o.w.. You can see more photos of this home, fill out an application and if pre-approved schedule a tour. Your Zillow application will cost $29.00 and you have unlimited applications within 30 days and you can submit for any home on Zillow. Thank you for your interest in McCall Properties.<br>
